                <Image   Margin="0,5"  x:Name="imgPhoto" Grid.Column="3" Width="64" Height="64" HorizontalAlignment="Right"  Source="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/5/59/User-avatar.svg/1024px-User-avatar.svg.
                         "></Image>
